comments.content:
The first sample is from Details Magazine, ok!? The type is September, a custom design by Hubert Jochan!

[http://www.hubertjocham.de/](http://web.archive.org/web/20080907013633/http:/www.hubertjocham.de/ "http://www.hubertjocham.de/")
i wasn’t aware it was a custom font, i thought it was along the lines of a franklin gothic. Thanks for your help.
